nodes.text: SL33-Z was a sales droid who was sent by Ma'Haffee Shipyard to represent them at the Cularin Trade Show during the Clone Wars.

He was of a very rare design and consisted of a large immobile computer station that controlled eight humanoid droid salesmen drones. These drones resembled B1-Series battle droids, but with display screens on their heads. They escorted customers around the showroom to show them the company's products and SL33-Z was programmed to make them use a hard-sell appoach to these interactions.
